column1: Today we are running two expeirments.  First experiment is to track product production in the suspension vs biocomposite
Second experiment is to compare drying in OTA1 with WT
Starting spinning first three bottles at 815am
first three bottles only gave of 910uL, I inoculated too late on wednesday. We had to spin a 4th down while leaving the first pellet in the chamber starting at 930
4th bottle of cells finished spinning down at 10:30 with 500uL of cells
It seems odd that the first 3 bottles only gave 910uL of cells while the 4th bottle, even though it grew for a couple more hours than the other 3 bottles, gave 500uL of cells.
